# ripgrep configuration
# https://github.com/BurntSushi/ripgrep/blob/master/GUIDE.md#configuration-file

# Case-insensitive unless the pattern contains uppercase letters.
--smart-case

# Show column numbers alongside line numbers.
--column

# Follow symlinks.
--follow

# Truncate long lines in output rather than printing raw bytes.
--max-columns=200
--max-columns-preview
